summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Woodlawn Avenue from North Sixty-fifth Street to Ravenna Boulevard, et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 21172, creating Local Improvement District No. 2078 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing the delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
